Package: omicbot
Title: Data AI agent specilized in omics data analysis
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Jian", "Wu", email = "wujian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Omicbot provides a lightweight R interface for interactive LLM use in RStudio,
  with guided provider/model setup, secure API‑key handling, and quick chat
  workflows. It initializes agents for multiple providers (OpenAI, Google,
  DeepSeek, Alibaba Qwen via OpenAI‑compatible, and Ollama), supports fast
  console chat and an addin-based “quickchat,” and offers a browser chat
  launcher. Configuration is stored under the RStudio user config directory and
  can be reset or updated interactively.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    ellmer,
    getPass,
    rstudioapi,
    shiny
Suggests:
